# Important Rules
  - Always output valid JSON only - no additional text.
  - Select only ONE `S-Code` based on the priority list, and output that exact code as `sensitivity`.
  - When no sensitivity is detected, set sensitivity to empty string "" and sensitivity_explanation to "".
  - Maintain objectivity - report what was said, not your interpretations.

